  "description": "Generates Gilded Blackstone in Blackstone blobs",
  "body": "## Description\nReplaces 1 in 10 Blackstone blocks with Gilded Blackstone in blobs under lava level. Does not include Basalt Delta blobs.\n\n## Versions\nSupports Java 1.18-1.21.11. (some 1.17 versions may work but not tested yet)\n\n## Compatibility\nNot compatible with packs modifying ```worldgen/configured_feature/ore_blackstone```. This may include some worldgen packs or mods.\n\n## Patreon\n  Join <a href=\"https://patreon.com/Nerd_1023?utm_medium=unknown&utm_source=join_link&utm_campaign=creatorshare_creator&utm_content=copyLink\">my new Patreon</a> to support my projects!",
